Shader-O-matic
==============

About
-----
A small tool to test and develop quickly shaders (vertex, tessellation, geometry and fragment).

Authors
-------
* Emmanuel Durand <emmanueldurand@gmail.com>

Project URL
-----------
https://github.com/paperManu/shader-o-matic

Installation notes
------------------
Quick walkthrough for installation on Ubuntu 14.04 and up:
    sudo apt-add-repository ppa:pyglfw/pyglfw
    sudo apt-get install libglfw3
    sudo apt-get install libopencv-dev
    ./autogen.sh && ./configure
    make && sudo make install
